</a><p>Specifically, GPT-3 shaped the ending of this story. It planted the idea that the Voice should disable Trin’s voice, which made me rethink the entire theme. This wasn’t about how addictive a brain implant could be, but rather, about how to find the courage to stick your neck out after being beset by oppressive organizations for your entire life.</p>